.Dd February 13, 2023
.Dt ZPOOL-RECYCLE 8
.Os
.
.Sh NAME
.Nm zpool-recycle
.Nd recycle space used by shared log ZIL chains
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm zpool
.Cm recycle
.Op Fl n
.Op Ar pool
.
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Iterate over the list of ZIL chains in the provided shared log pool,
and delete the chains belonging to pools that are not currently imported.
Prints out a list of pool GUIDs for the deleted chains.
.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width "-n"
.It Fl n
Do not actually perform any deletions, just print out the list of pool
GUIDs that would be affected.
.El
